    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but the suspension is starting to feel a bit soft and there is a minor slow leak in the power steering fluid. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard. It is a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation who doesn't mind some aesthetic imperfections and routine upcoming maintenance.",
