    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sustained aesthetic appeal. This specimen has undergone a rigorous professional inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and safety. Offering a refined driving experience and a well-preserved interior, this vehicle represents an exceptional acquisition for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of reliability and sophistication. Prepared for immediate delivery and long-term service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
