    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape! It runs like a dream and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice if you want something high-quality and dependable without that brand-new price tag. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how great it feels on the road. Drop me a message if you're interested!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
