      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving masterpiece. The S54 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, pulling cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. Maintenance is up to date, including a documented valve shim adjustment and cooling system refresh. The chassis has been inspected for rear subframe fatigue and remains structurally sound. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the suspension geometry is precise, and the hydraulic steering rack provides excellent feedback. This is a driver-focused machine with the mechanical integrity required for spirited use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
